<DATE>
<P>
January 15, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
<P>
Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Page 3; Calendar Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
